window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Some secrets prefer to stay buried. </p> <p>When Dean’s closest ally is kidnapped by an ancient race, his grief threatens to turn to madness. With the support of his friends, he embarks on a mission to get his loved one back, and stop the eventual destruction of the known Universe. </p> <p>But Dean can’t do it without solving an age-old mystery. He must find the real Theos this time, and he’ll stop at nothing to accomplish that. </p> <p>Join the Survivors as they battle for every race in existence. </p> <p><i>The Theos </i>is a tale of love, adventure, deception, and above all else: surviving.</p>"; 
